name: Freedom - Self Potrait #1
description:
The first NFT collection of "Self Potrait" series. 

Is there really a human being who is truly free? If anyone says that freedom is real, then that person doesn't realize how constrained we are in this life. Our voices are often limited, what we do is bound by norms and morals. Is that called freedom?
